verbose_text: Milder SCs extraction conditions using decreasing (4-1 mg/mg) digitonin-to-protein ratios, revealed no differences in the levels of SC I+ III 2 + IV 1 between COX7A2L-KO and WT cells (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY), but a clear decrease in the abundance of larger SCs (indicated with an asterisk) in COX7A2L-KO cells (XREF_FIG), further suggesting that COX7A2L may be required for the normal assembly or stability of these megastructures.
